title: 2022 United States gubernatorial elections
added: [[Governor of New Hampshire|Governor]] [[Chris Sununu]] was re-elected in the [[2020 New Hampshire gubernatorial election]]. He is eligible to run for re-election, but has not yet stated whether he will do so.

[[Governor of Vermont|Governor]] [[Phil Scott (politician)|Phil Scott]] was re-elected in the [[2020 Vermont gubernatorial election]]. He is eligible to run for re-election, but has not yet stated whether he will do so.
